title: Palm Springs Open
text: The Palm Springs Open was a <a href="golf">golf</a> tournament on the <a href="LPGA%20Tour">LPGA Tour</a>, played only in 1953. It was played at the Tamarisk Country Club in <a href="Palm%20Springs%2C%20California">Palm Springs, California</a>. <a href="Jackie%20Pung">Jackie Pung</a> won the event.
